the Paralympic movement,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2635, \"end\": 2654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paralympics No.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"7 on home soil - I think it will be a dream.\\\"\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scott Stump is a trending reporter and the writer of the daily newsletter This is TODAY (which you shouldsubscribe to here!)\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2731, \"end\": 2736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"score\": 0.994536265198092, \"rank\": 0.004839529205627581, \"text\": \"Scott\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Walter_Scott\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"that brings the day's news, health tips, parenting stories, recipes and uplifting stories right to your inbox.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been a regular contributor for TODAY.com since 2011, producing features and news for pop culture, parents, politics, health, style, food and pretty much everything else.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"score\": 0.9998395956472322, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TODAY.com\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_program)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_(American_TV_progr